# NostrComments

**Comment freely on every website — without censorship**

NostrComments adds a decentralized, uncensorable comment layer to any website using the Nostr protocol.

No servers. No moderation. No deletion. Ever.

### Features
- Works on every website (news websites, YouTube, Reddit, Twitter (X), …)
- Connect with any Nostr signer (Alby, nos2x, GetAlby, etc.)
- Upvotes/downvotes (NIP-25)
- Search, sort, pagination
- Community moderation (auto-hide heavily downvoted comments)
- Fully open source & privacy-friendly

### Install
- Firefox: [Download .xpi](https://github.com/briskness-byte/NostrComments/releases/latest)
- Chrome/Edge/Brave: [Chrome Web Store] (coming soon) or load unpacked

### Source code
You’re looking at it! Feel free to fork, audit, improve.

